         MACRO                                                                  
&L       REG   &N                                                               
.*       RE-DONE 4/79, JDN;  Modified, 11/85, Niz                               
.*               3/21/94 jws  Change @&L length from 0 to 1                     
.*               7/19/94 ral  Change @&L length from 1 back to 0                
.*                            Done to make PMOV work correctly                  
         GBLA  &$REG#                                                           
         GBLB  &$OK                                                             
&L       EQU   &N,&N,C'#'                                                       
&LOC     SETC  '&SYSLOC'                                                        
         PUSH  NOGEN                                                            
        $RGLKUP &N                                                              
         AIF   (&$OK).DO                                                        
&$REG#   SETA  &N                                                               
.DO      ANOP                                                                   
$$$@R&$REG#  DSECT                                                              
@&L      EQU   *,0,C'@'                                                         
         AIF   ('&LOC' EQ '').EXIT                                              
&LOC     LOCTR                                                                  
.EXIT    POP   PRINT                                                            
         MEND                                                                   
